selectors are of two types : basic and advanced.

in basic selectors we have 5 selectors:element , id , class , attribute and universal selectors.

---element selectors:
 mein hum kisi particular element pr css lgate hain like p{}, div{}.

---id selectors:
 jab humare pass multiple element hain but hum sb pr css nhi lgane chahte sirf kisi particular pr css lgane chahte hain then we will use id selectors by giving a id to a tag.
it is represented by #.
this id has to be unique and be aware it's a good habit of a good developer of not assigning the same id to a different tag.
****** never use same id.

----class selectors:
 jab 1 change ko more than one place display krna ho tab we use class selectors.
hum 1 se jyada baar class assign kr skte hain ethically.

-----Attribute selectors:
isme attribute ki help se css lgate hain like href is our attribute to uski help se lgayenge css.

----Universal selector:
har cheez ko select kro irrespective of anything.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Universal selector are of 4 types:
1. combinators:
   i) Descendant
   ii) child
   iii) adjacent sibling
   iv) General sibling

2. pseudo classes
3. structural pseudo elements.
4. String Matching 

****----Combinator:do cheez se milke bna h.

----descendant:iss case m hum kitne b level neeche jaake check kr skte hain.

-----Child: isme just neeche wali level ko check krte hain kya vo defined syntax se match kr rhi h ya nhi.
represented as: div>p{}

----adjacent sibling: jinka parent same ho unhe adjacent sibling kehte hain.

---General sibling: jo sibling same level pr hote hain unhe general sibling kehte hain .
inke parent common hona jruri nhi h , parents  sibling hone chahiye.
###always sibling right side m dekhe jaate hain

****pseudo classes:
some are- :hover, :visited , :active, :focus.
---:hover-cursor ko upar laao to change ho.
---:active- jab b hum click krenge tb kya change aayega.
----:visited- ye btata h ki tum yahan tum visit kr chuke ho ya nhi.
----:focus-
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

***pseudo elements***
pseudo classes m : ye lgate hain aur elements m  :: 
psuedo classes inline/block pr lga skte hain but elements m sirf blovk kaam krega.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
****STRING MATCHING****
1. starts with ^=
2. ends with $=
3 present anywhere *=